    • Constructor Detail

      • MillionSongDataSubset

        public MillionSongDataSubset​(java.lang.String jsonFilePath)
        One object of class FoothillTunesStore parses a JSON data set with a given json file and stores each entry in an array 'tunes' and acts as a iTune song store. It provides methods showing all the songs in our personal tunes library, adding new songs in our tunes collection by title selection, making a play list of a certain duration. One object of class MillionSongDatSubset parses a JSON data set with a given file path. Stores each entry into a SongEntry object.
        Parameters:
        jsonFilePath - The JSON file to parse.
